601
00:30:52,577 --> 00:30:53,577
Barbecue.

602
00:30:53,657 --> 00:30:54,697
Barbecue?

603
00:30:55,657 --> 00:30:57,256
Why is there no smoke smell at all?

604
00:30:57,256 --> 00:30:58,257
