835
00:43:44,096 --> 00:43:45,096
Well...

836
00:44:09,976 --> 00:44:13,784
(I'm the knight with severed hands,)

837
00:44:13,784 --> 00:44:21,400
(but it doesn't affect
the freshness of the rose.)

